cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.MM, cs.CR, cs.AI 

The paper deals with face anti-spoofing, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves the use of deep neural networks and discriminative feature learning, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.LG) and multimedia (cs.MM). The problem of spoof attacks also falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR). Finally, the use of domain adaptation and robustness against variability factors suggests the involvement of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
